These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: rock, reggae, r&b, salsa, house, dubstep, punk
City: venice, hannover, boston, san-francisco, nizza, rome, london
 1. the fan rock is between the fan salsa and the fan punk##2
 2. the fan reggae is in the middle##1
 3. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 4. the fan house is between the person traveling to boston and the person traveling to nizza##2
 5. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 6. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the fan salsa##1
 7. the person traveling to venice is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person traveling to boston##2
 8. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the fan punk##1
 9. the fan house is on the left of the fan dubstep##1
10. the fan house is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
11. the fan dubstep is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | rock | punk | reggae    | r&b | house   | dubstep    |
| City         | rome  | hannover   | san-francisco | venice | boston   | london | nizza |

