.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
House: ranch-style, gothic-revival, wooden, farmhouse, townhouse, cottage, victorian
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: zombie, western, adventure, family, drama, martial-arts, scientific
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left##1
2. the wooden house is between the cottage house and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
3. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the victorian house is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the gothic-revival house is in the middle##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
8. the townhouse house is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
9. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| House          | townhouse | wooden | cottage | gothic-revival | victorian | ranch-style      | farmhouse  |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | family  | scientific     | adventure     | drama  | zombie | western |

