 3. the person traveling to hamburg is the person playing bridge##1
 4. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 6. the person playing poker is the person traveling to prague##1
 7. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 8. the person traveling to miami is between the person traveling to boston and the person playing poker##2
 9. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
10. the person playing whist is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Game   | bridge | snooker | scrabble | whist   | poker | monopoly | mah-jongg |
