 3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in july##2
 7. the person who's sport is july-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 8. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
10. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in november##2
11. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
