5. the person drinking soy-milk is in the middle##1
6. the indonesian is on the left of the colombian##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
8. the indonesian is on the right of the nigerian##1
9. the person drinking cola is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Nationality   | chinese | german     | nigerian | indonesian | colombian | malaysian  | egyptian |
| Beverage     | iced-tea | sprite | juice   | soy-milk     | cola    | tea | hot-chocolate   |

